{"tid":1674730,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 有冇人屋企好似我咁窮","createTime":"2019-10-25T11:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T10:55:12.000Z","uid":1734,"like":19,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfb11cac938681bdce21906e86e0643af9b342a","tid":1674730,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"自細都未試過有餐包飯食 細個d奶粉都係沖勁多水 <br />\n溝到好稀咁食 <br />\n<br />\n到小學 多數人都係學校訂飯或者帶飯   我都係每日食生命面包加飲水  最開心個日就會有半條蕉食下 另一半留比細妹 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到中學 返part time 大多比曬屋企 自己都係留一百蚊一個星期用 包搭車 有時唔夠錢唯有行返學 （ 我住深水埗 學校係荃灣 ）  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到以家18 歲都未食過自助餐 放題 打邊勞 生日蛋糕都未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企 4 個人住 100 尺劏房  屋企上網都係偷隔離 到18 歲 女仔都唔敢識 好驚比人笑 點算好 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs 我地係新移民 政府食屎啦 咁耐都唔幫我地"},{"pid":"0d37d872bd7715c694fe3be2780e067c3c021105","tid":1674730,"uid":314136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebdb7b3984f15a29284d09b0da196f5f65c442c","tid":1674730,"uid":46720,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬一日可以開幾多個膠post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a253faef2c99cf676db7b3bb7df54cb454893d93","tid":1674730,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"eebdb7b3984f15a29284d09b0da196f5f65c442c","tid":1674730,"uid":46720,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬一日可以開幾多個膠post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:22:25.000Z","msg":"今次真事分享 好